{"type":"message","id":"90e601ab","parentId":"218d81e9","timestamp":"2026-07-18T12:25:18.128Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_plcajhib","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"schema\": \"2.0\",\n  \"description\": \"CHG Trigger Rules \\u2014 Yoda monitors these and raises CHG+Telegram alert when triggered.\",\n  \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-07-10T11:57:00+10:00\",\n  \"lastUpdatedBy\": \"Yoda\",\n  \"changeNote\": \"CHG-0859: Added TRIGGER-01 sub-action 01-CLOUD-OUTAGE-PROBE \\u2014 Ollama Cloud outage probe + local OC2 fallback, deferred from CHG-0858 outage-detect no-op.\",\n  \"triggers\": {\n    \"TRIGGER-01\": {\n      \"name\": \"OC2 Arrival \\u2014 Master Gate\",\n      \"condition\": \"OC2-A and OC2-B physically arrive\",\n      \"detection\": \"manual \\u2014 Ken notifies Yoda\",\n      \"eta\": \"6\\u201313 Jul 2026\",\n      \"status\": \"not_applicable\",\n      \"firedAt\": null,\n      \"closureNote\": \"OC2-A/B arrival gate closed; only OC2A commissioned as single-node PROD. HA pair deferred. See CHG-1783.\",\n      \"description\": \"OC2 arrival is now the master gate. All OC2-era actions are sequenced as sub-actions under TRIGGER-01, executed in priority order after hardware is online.\",\n      \"subActions\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-PHYSICAL\",\n          \"name\": \"Hardware Setup\",\n          \"priority\": \"critical\",\n          \"action\": \"Unbox OC2-A + OC2-B. Connect power, network, Tailscale. Verify both nodes reachable on tailnet.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-OPENCLAW\",\n          \"name\": \"OpenClaw Install on OC2-A/B\",\n          \"priority\": \"critical\",\n          \"action\": \"Install OpenClaw v2026.5.27+ on OC2-A (primary) and OC2-B (standby). Configure HIVE HA pair. Deploy tech agent fleet (~10 agents: Yoda, Atlas, Thrawn, Forge, Lando, Mon Mothma, Warden, Ahsoka, Luthen; Shield/Lex/Sage stay here). Krennic parked.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-CLAUDE-RESTORE\",\n          \"name\": \"CLAUDE RESTORE \\u2014 Anthropic API Key Re-provisioning\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Ken provides new Anthropic API key. Execute SOP: (1) Store in Keychain as 'ainchors-anthropic-api-key', (2) Add auth.profiles.anthropic:default to openclaw.json, (3) Add anthropic model aliases, (4) Update model-policy.json whitelist, (5) Run validate-fallback-chain.sh, (6) Restore agent primary models from claude-restore-config.json.\",\n          \"linkedChgs\": [\n            \"CHG-0349\",\n            \"CHG-0373\",\n            \"CHG-0393\"\n          ],\n          \"linkedTkts\": [\n            \"TKT-0165\",\n            \"TKT-0241\"\n          ],\n          \"note\": \"Folded from standalone TRIGGER-14 per Ken directive 2026-05-29. Claude Restore now gates on OC2 arrival \\u2014 no point restoring on OC1 when platform is about to migrate.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-PLATFORM-SEPARATION\",\n          \"name\": \"Platform Separation \\u2014 OC1 Business Standalone\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Execute Platform Separation per approved option paper. Phase 1: Wipe OC1, fresh OpenClaw install, deploy 6 business agents (Aria lead + Shield/Lex/Sage duplicated + Spark + Forge-ops). Phase 2: OC2 tech platform validated \\u22651 week before OC1 wipe. Phase 3: Cutover Angie/KL team to OC1 business node. Phase 4: Stabilisation.\",\n          \"linkedDocs\": [\n            \"docs/options/Platform-Separation-Business-Stream-Option-Paper-v1.0.md\",\n            \"docs/options/Platform-Separation-Business-Stream-Feasibility-Assessment-v1.0.md\"\n          ],\n          \"kenDecisions\": [\n            \"C1: Second OpenClaw license \\u2705\",\n            \"C2: Separate Ollama Cloud sub \\u2705\",\n            \"C3: New Google Workspace for tech \\u2705\"\n          ],\n          \"acceptedRisks\": [\n            \"No SRE on business node\",\n            \"Governance Triad divergence\",\n            \"Double maintenance overhead\"\n          ],\n          \"note\": \"Platform Separation approved 2026-05-29. Phase 0 prep can start now. Full migration gated on OC2 arrival + validation.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-PG-MIGRATION\",\n          \"name\": \"PostgreSQL Migration OC1 \\u2192 OC2\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Restore PG from OC1 backup to OC2-A. Configure HA replication to OC2-B. Validate all 32 tables, ticket state, cost history. Slim PG on OC1 (business-only tables or PG-free).\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-A\",\n          \"name\": \"qwen3.5:cloud Reassessment\",\n          \"priority\": \"low\",\n          \"action\": \"Re-benchmark qwen3.5:cloud on OC2. Re-test with think:false on all 5 benchmark tasks. If avg latency \\u226420s \\u2192 approve for async/batch Tier 2. If still fails \\u2192 close out permanently.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-B\",\n          \"name\": \"Orchestrator MD Version Bump\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Version bump SOUL.md + YODA_RULES.md + ORCHESTRATOR.md to reflect OC2 architecture, HA state, Gemma4:26b local inference, Platform Separation.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-C\",\n          \"name\": \"SecretRefs Keychain Integration\",\n          \"priority\": \"medium\",\n          \"action\": \"Implement SecretRefs with macOS Keychain integration (TKT-0228). Migrate all API keys from hardcoded config to structured SecretRefs.\",\n          \"ticket\": \"TKT-0228\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-NEW-WORKSPACE\",\n          \"name\": \"Tech Stream Google Workspace\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Create new Google Workspace for tech stream (C3). Migrate Yoda/tech agent auth from kenmun@ainchors.com to new account. Aria keeps kenmun@ on OC1 business node.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-CLOUD-OUTAGE-PROBE\",\n          \"name\": \"Ollama Cloud Outage Probe + Local OC2 Fallback\",\n          \"priority\": \"high\",\n          \"action\": \"Design and implement a proper Ollama Cloud outage probe (not localhost:11434). On cloud unreachable, trigger automatic fallback to local OC2 models (gemma4:26b / gemma4:31b-coding-mtp-bf16 per TRIGGER-03). Re-enable outage-detect.sh logic with cloud-aware probe. Validate against model-policy.json and run full outage/standby drill.\",\n          \"dependencies\": [\n            \"TRIGGER-02\",\n            \"TRIGGER-03\"\n          ],\n          \"linkedChgs\": [\n            \"CHG-0858\",\n            \"CHG-0859\"\n          ],\n          \"linkedTkts\": [\n            \"TKT-0973\"\n          ],\n          \"note\": \"Deferred from CHG-0858 because outage-detect.sh probed localhost:11434, which is invalid for Ollama Cloud and risks false standby. Local fallback requires OC2 HA and Gemma4 local validation (TRIGGER-03).\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": \"01-OC2A-PRODUCTION\",\n          \"name\": \"OC2A Fresh Install \\u2014 Option 4 Strong Separation\",\n          \"priority\": \"critical\",\n          \"action\": \"Execute docs/plans/OC2A-Fresh-Install-Plan-v1.0.md. OC2A becomes self-governing full production Nexus; OC1 demoted to non-privileged sandbox with no admin path to OC2A. Phases sequenced as TKT-0757 through TKT-0762. Begin after 01-PHYSICAL and 01-OPENCLAW complete.\",\n          \"linkedChgs\": [\n            \"CHG-0868\"\n          ],\n          \"linkedTkts\": [\n            \"TKT-0757\",\n            \"TKT-0758\",\n            \"TKT-0759\",\n            \"TKT-0760\",\n            \"TKT-0761\",\n            \"TKT-0762\"\n          ],\n          \"note\": \"Replaces prior Platform Separation sub-action (01-PLATFORM-SEPARATION) which assumed OC1 business-only node. New model: OC2A full production, OC1 sandbox only, strong separation.\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"TRIGGER-02\": {\n    